b0565dc461e4bdb2213d74d7fa","tid":805618,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb440b3631cbb349499da1921fbb2361ea4b25b1","tid":805618,"uid":189243,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"有錯全都是別人的錯，歪理連篇，符合國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d1e469ba1ef3f7b143a6646a50212c481082d","tid":805618,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪用騰訊旗下既wechat同記者訴苦"},{"pid":"ee58afd7e6d290229f5cd27695beaefa9b5543df","tid":805618,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"唔識教跟住重想賴game<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a5eda7f1307bdc40f68fba0ce6fd05d2f3fb02","tid":805618,"uid":147198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180904/640_047b50009a6eee7e18e3ba8d5a237261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180904%2F640_047b50009a6eee7e18e3ba8d5a237261.jpg&h=c75c2fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國江蘇海門市一名13歲少年徐天賜，日前在親友家從4樓跳下身亡，由於他在死前正在俗稱「吃雞」的大逃殺遊戲《絕地求生》，母親氣憤直指「我兒子絕對是遊戲害死的，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對不會是其他原因的</span></span>」，揚言要告到遊戲公司破產。<br />\n<br />\n據《看看新聞》報導，徐天賜的父母都在南非經商，家境不錯，他在8月29日深夜11時多還在和同學一起玩《絕地求生》，卻在8月30日凌晨突然跳下4樓身亡，母親郁禮花表示，兒子開朗、善良、人見人愛，根本沒有自殺的理由，唯一可能就是他在遊戲結束後大腦仍沉浸在遊戲裡，所以才會嘗試去做遊戲裡那種跳樓只會損血而不會死亡的行為。<br />\n<br />\n郁禮花痛批《絕地求生》裡「就是叫小孩跳樓，沒關係的，出一點血，人又會活過來」，兒子就是受到影響才會跳樓看是不是能活過來，她表示自己將會對遊戲公司提告，「我要告到它破產，告到它把用人家生命換過來的錢，全部要還給人家。」<br />\n<br />\n網友們則感嘆「父母不陪伴孩子，還怨遊戲」、「不起訴賣手機、賣電腦的嗎」、「他跳樓前還呼吸空氣呢，您要不把地球也告了」、「吃雞你從高一點的地方跳下來一樣會死」、「求求你們管管孩子、救救遊戲」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180904/1423410/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180904%2F1423410%2F&d=0cSX4lvwS2oF0OhBj3LQO6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=78b1a840\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180904%2F1423410%2F&h=a4d3a6ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180904/1423410/</a></blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n咁肯定自己個仔唔係弱智咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e34581ce905adf03c1258b1b0d1bd4be543dd46","tid":805618,"uid":48724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4db84d24faea933bf98bd873ec3b317f1efe3459","tid":805618,"uid":40049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"尋釁滋事，叫佢老母玩定「逆轉裁判」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ddd38f092abcbf0f25b49b7c630a4ad216f498","tid":805618,"uid":158372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"13歲仔都唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41144857883812689a03a2a8d1fe038cd0101658","tid":805618,"uid":181767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"達爾文得獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87901543ef9203380de5acc0da78a20c19245a73","tid":805618,"